<br>
However, I think the actual concept of the bazaar has somehow missed a few of you guys.  Im up there today looking for an item and there are like 20 people spaming &quot;WTS...&quot;  including Alremon.<br>
<br>
Now i could be wrong, but spaming auctions to a zone population that is 99% afk seems pretty fucking stupid.  <br>
<br>
Further, I love to see Alremon just spaming his ass off bc now everyone can just dial up his prices, compare and see how absolutely fucking ridiculous he is, oh you too Blurz and Beardo.<br>
<br>
I mean i bought a runed etched icefang thang for 3k, this dumbass has it for 10k and thinks that bc I like him so much im gonna choose him when im comparison shopping.<br>
<br>
Thats what great about the Bazaar, now i dont have to deal with jackass, no life, career, mofos who think that they can sell items for 200% over the average price.  55k for a fungi, OMG that is freakin hilarious, and i really want to meet the dumbass who paid that price.   With the Bazaar, I just have to wait a little and someone else will always sell lower.  Yes even the high end items.  take a look for yourself.<br>
<br>
BTW log on now, i bet money that Alremon is up there spaming away, trying to relive the good old days when he would lock people up with his 40 lines of absolute foolishness.  Its a cry for help people.<br>
<br>
One final thing, Hey Waat, you need to get into Beardo's intervention.  You need a date bad, bro.  Go to Vegas or Reno or AC or Biloxi or CT Indian Res... Anything, please just leave the damn Bazaar, all you do is cause serious freakin lag.  If you dont, ill come play your game and play 10k a hand and put your punk ass out of business.  Check your odds fool.   They are not even close to Vegas type odds.  Name a casino game where you get double payout on each hand, have a 20% chance to hit, and only have to buy in 1 time for 3 chances.  Please someone tell me, bc im on a plane this weekend.  All i got to do is hit two or three times and your bankroll is toast.<br>
<br>
